The repo contains submodules. To checkout:

  git clone git@github.com:stevef00/puppet-repo.git
  cd puppet-repo.git
  git pull --recurse-submodules
  git submodule update --init --recursive

Adding a new submodule:

  First, add the submodule:

  - git submodule add URL PATH

    git submodule add https://github.com/gutocarvalho/puppet-puppetagent.git modules/puppetagent

  Then check the staged changes (should be an addition to .gitmodules and the commit reference for the module.
  If it looks ok, commit and push.


